                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>ARGUMENT.</emph>
            </head>
            <lb/>
            <p>How a Ship having passed the Line was driven by<lb/>Storms to the cold Country
              towards the South Pole;<lb/>and how from thence she made her course to
              the<lb/>tropical Latitude of the Great Pacific Ocean; and<lb/>of the strange things
              that befell; and in what<lb/>manner the Ancyent Marinere came back to his<lb/>own
              Country.</p>
         </argument>
